Brilliant direction, Etienne. Here's how we can structure a **GitHub Pages starter kit** that integrates:

- The full **Cisco Junior Cybersecurity Analyst Path**
- A modular **reading plan**
- Equivalent tracks from **TryHackMe** and **EC-Council**
- Optional **badge tracker** and **sprint planner**

---

## 🧱 GitHub Pages Starter Kit Structure

```
/learning-paths/
│
├── index.md
├── roadmap.md
├── badge-tracker.md
├── sprint-planner.md
│
├── cisco/
│   ├── overview.md
│   ├── modules/
│   │   ├── intro-to-cybersecurity.md
│   │   ├── networking-basics.md
│   │   ├── networking-devices.md
│   │   ├── endpoint-security.md
│   │   ├── network-defense.md
│   │   ├── cyber-threat-management.md
│   │   ├── career-path-exam.md
│   └── reading-plan.md
│
├── tryhackme/
│   ├── overview.md
│   ├── modules/
│   │   ├── presecurity.md
│   │   ├── foundations.md
│   │   ├── soc-track.md
│   │   ├── pentester-track.md
│   │   ├── engineer-track.md
│   └── certification.md
│
├── eccouncil/
│   ├── overview.md
│   ├── essentials.md
│   ├── certifications.md
│   ├── cost-summary.md
│   └── free-courses.md
```

---

## 🔗 index.md

```markdown
# 🚀 Cybersecurity Learning Hub

Welcome to your modular cybersecurity learning kit. This GitHub Pages site integrates:

- Cisco Junior Cybersecurity Analyst Path
- TryHackMe Career Tracks
- EC-Council Essentials & Certifications
- Reading Plans, Badge Tracker, and Sprint Planner

Start with the [Roadmap](./roadmap.md) or jump into a provider-specific path:
- [Cisco Path](./cisco/overview.md)
- [TryHackMe Path](./tryhackme/overview.md)
- [EC-Council Path](./eccouncil/overview.md)
```

---

## 🧭 roadmap.md

```markdown
# 🧭 Cybersecurity Roadmap Overview

| Provider     | Entry-Level Path             | Intermediate Track         | Advanced Track               |
|--------------|------------------------------|-----------------------------|------------------------------|
| Cisco        | CCST Cybersecurity           | CyberOps Associate          | CCNP/CCIE Security           |
| TryHackMe    | Presecurity + Foundations    | SOC / Pentester / Engineer | CPTS Certification           |
| EC-Council   | Essentials Series (EHE, DFE) | CEH / CND / CHFI            | LPT / ECSA / CISA / CISM     |

Use this roadmap to guide your sprint planning and badge tracking.
```

---

## 🏁 badge-tracker.md

```markdown
# 🏁 Badge Tracker

Track your progress across platforms:

| Platform     | Badge / Cert Name           | Status | Date Earned |
|--------------|-----------------------------|--------|-------------|
| Cisco        | CCST Cybersecurity          | ☐      |             |
| TryHackMe    | Presecurity Completion      | ☐      |             |
| TryHackMe    | SAL1 / PT1 Certification    | ☐      |             |
| EC-Council   | Ethical Hacking Essentials  | ☐      |             |
| EC-Council   | CEH                         | ☐      |             |
```

