## ⏱️ sprint-planner.md

```markdown
# ⏱️ Sprint Planner

Plan your weekly learning sprints:

| Week | Focus Area                  | Module / Book                  | Goal                        | Status |
|------|-----------------------------|--------------------------------|-----------------------------|--------|
| 1    | Cybersecurity Fundamentals  | Cisco Intro + Brooks Essentials| Complete module + 2 chapters| ☐      |
| 2    | Networking Basics           | Cisco + Jill West              | Finish labs + 3 chapters    | ☐      |
| 3    | Endpoint Security           | Cisco + Sammons                | Complete labs + quiz        | ☐      |
| 4    | SOC Skills                  | TryHackMe SOC Track + Murdoch  | Begin detection labs        | ☐      |
```

---

## 🧩 Deployment Tips

- Host this structure on GitHub Pages using a Jekyll theme or Docsify.
- Link each module to external labs (TryHackMe, Cisco NetAcad, CodeRed).
- Use GitHub Issues or Projects to track progress collaboratively.
- Add `.yml` config for sidebar navigation if using Docsify or MkDocs.

